title: Kings of Leon - B-Sides & Rarities Volumes 1&2
description:
Kings of Leon: B-Sides and Rarities Vol. 1

Track List:

1. Woo Hoo
2. Head To Toe
3. My Third House
4. California Waiting (Alternate Version)
5. Dusty (Piano Version)
6. Wicker Chair
7. Talihina Sky (Alternate Version)
8. Molly's Hangover
9. Where Nobody Knows (Aha Shake Heartbreak Bonus Track)
10. On Call (Grum Disco Remix)
11. Milk (Stretch & Vern Remix)
12. My Party (Kenna & Chad Hugo Remix)

INFO:

	I decided to make this compilation a few weeks ago out of anticipation of the new album. I acquired the bonus tracks from the "B-Sides PLUS!!" torrent that has been floating around for a while. I added a few more tracks which were either from other torrents or ripped from stream sites, and added some artwork so it looks good in your iTunes library. Quality varies, but all are decent/good quality rips. The "Kings of Leon: B-Sides and Rarities" compilations are something I am going to continue to make. Volume 2 has been started, but I will wait to upload it as soon as those iTunes exclusive tracks pop up somewhere.

INFO: 

Like the last compilation except with different rare tracks. Looks great in iTunes. Quality varies as a few of these were stream rips. Hope everyone enjoys it. It was a bitch finding these! I am working on volume three right now. It will feature Frontier City and the Bucket CSS Mix as well as several other rare tracks.
